OL,3,CGas company denies charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion at family home
OL,6,FJersey Gas has pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fthe charge of breaching Jersey's
OL,8,Fhealth and safety at work law.
OL,10,FThe charges relate to the house
OL,11,Fexplosion at a property in Elizabeth
OL,12,FVillas, Mont Pinel in St Saviour on 26
OL,13,FJune 2024.
OL,15,FJersey Gas, which trades under the
OL,16,Fname Island Energy, was summoned to
OL,17,Fthe island's Magistrate's Court
OL,18,Ffollowing the Health and Safety
OL,19,FInspectorate's investigation.
