OL,4,Cexplosion at family home
OL,6,FDarryl Goddard, the firm's Managing
OL,7,FDirector, appeared in court to enter
OL,8,Fthe plea on Thursday morning.
OL,10,FThe charge facing the firm falls under
OL,11,FArticle 21 of the Health and Safety at
OL,12,FWork (Jersey) Law 1989 for failing in
OL,13,Ftheir duties to "ensure the health and
OL,14,Fsafety of persons not in their
OL,15,Femployment, including the public".
