OL,3,CGas company denies charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion at family home
OL,6,FThe prosecutor, Crown Advocate Paul
OL,7,FLee, stated that the company was
OL,8,Faccused of failing to adhere to codes
OL,9,Fof practice in not properly
OL,10,Fdisconnecting old gas pipes, which led
OL,11,Fto gas accumulating inside the house
OL,12,Fand creating the conditions for the
OL,13,Fexplosion.
OL,15,FHe added that this was not the only
OL,16,Fproperty the prosecutions related to,
OL,17,Fand that there were a number of other
OL,18,Fproperties in a similar state.
