OL,3,CGas company denies charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion at family home
OL,6,FDefending Island Energy, Advocate Mike
OL,7,FPreston, said the firm denies failing
OL,8,Fto carry out operations that risked
OL,9,Fpeople's safety. He says that the
OL,10,Fcompany's actions were not the cause
OL,11,Fof the explosion.
OL,13,FHe added that this is not a "run of
OL,14,Fthe mill" case and there is an "awful
OL,15,Flot" of information to consider.
OL,17,FDue to the severity of the case, it
OL,18,Fwill be escalated to Jersey's Royal
OL,19,FCourt, where it will be heard on 6
OL,20,FFebruary 2026.
