OL,3,CGas company denies charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion at family home
OL,6,FA family of four, including children
OL,7,Faged two and five, were taken to the
OL,8,Fhospital after their house at Mont
OL,9,FPinel exploded in June last year.
OL,11,FThe children were unharmed, and the
OL,12,Fparents had non-life-changing
OL,13,Finjuries, but their home was partially
OL,14,Fdestroyed, and nearby properties were
OL,15,Fevacuated as a major incident was
OL,16,Fdeclared.
